# {{lb|fr|derogatory}} {{l|en|Harijan}}
#* {{quote-book|fr|author=Laetitia Colombani|title=Le Cerf-Volant|pageurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=obsxEAAAQBAJ&pg=PT53&lpg=PT53&p=42#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher=Grasset|page=43|year=2021
|passage=Un jour, Léna apprendra les punitions qu’on réserve aux enfants des hautes castes qui se hasardent à toucher un '''Harijan''', comme les appelait Gandhi. Elle entendra le témoignage de cet homme, contraint à l’âge de huit ans d’avaler de l’urine et de la bouse de vache pour expier sa faute.|t=One day, Lena will learn about the punishments reserved for high caste children who dare to touch a '''Harijan''', as Gandhi called them. She will hear the testimony of this man, who at eight years old was forced to consume cow urine and cowpat to expiate his error.}}

====Usage notes====
Now considered offensive to Dalits, as the term is considered patronising, ignorant, and seeking to assimilate them into Hindu nationalism.
